      <abstract abstract-type="short">
         <p>Differential Hox gene expression make the thumb special</p>
      </abstract>
      <abstract>
         <p>Asymmetric regulation of Hox gene expression pre-dates the appearance of tetrapod digits, and was co-opted in the development of 'thumbness'. This asymmetric expression correlates with independent morphological evolutionary variation of digit 1.</p>
